-- Misys to Buy Capital Markets Software Vendor Sophis for 435 Million Euros
-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 2010-11-12T07:10:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-12/misys-to-buy-capital-markets-software-vendor-sophis-for-435-million-euros.html
Misys Plc said it will acquire
capital markets software vendor Sophis for an enterprise value
of 435 million euros.  Misys also announced the tender offer terms for the return
to Misys shareholders of 670 million pounds of proceeds from the
sale by Misys of Allscripts shares.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  